features: SELECTED BAMBOO- Our bamboo shoe rack is made of 100% selected high quality bamboo, which is characterized by high density, toughness and renewability. Made of high temperature carbonization, the shoe rack is more sturdy compared to wooden shoe rack.

STRONG AND STABLE- All solid and high quality bamboo material, newly upgraded double screws hinge connection design, these ingenious features work together to create a quiqear shoe rack with strong load-bearing capacity and stable and sturdy.

FLEXIBLE STACKING AND COMBINATION- Perfect mortise and tenon construction design, can be stacked into different tiers of shoe racks. The unfolded size of the 3-tier shoe rack is 27.01'' * 11.02'' * 19.65'' , each tier can easily hold three pairs of adult shoes, and the bottom tier height is upgraded to 5.12 inches from the original 4.5 inches, which greatly increases the storage space at the bottom.

MULTIPLE USAGE SCENARIOS- Not just a shoe rack, but a multifunctional bamboo shelf. In addition to being a shoe rack for entryway, based on its lightweight, convenient and easy-to-move features, this bamboo shoe rack can be placed in the bedroom, bathroom, living room, kitchen, balcony more or a shoe rack for closet to hold your things.

EASY ASSEMBLY AND SERVICE- With the included complete toolkit and easy to understand instructions, we can get a complete shoe rack in just 5-10 minutes. Meanwhile, we provide you with comprehensive and thoughtful service, if you encounter any problems during the purchase process, you can contact us, we will provide you with detailed answers.

reviews.reviewText: Looks exactly like picture, it was very easy to assemble. It is a bit flimsy but that would only be a problem if you are putting a lot of heavy items on it. It works well for my shoe storage.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Quick and Easy Makeover
reviews.reviewText: My closet was an absolute mess. For the longest time I would just throw my shoes in the closet but over time it became a HUGE pile of shoes... it was awful and an eye sore, and in all honesty made it more difficult to put my shoes on. I found these to be the cheapest listings of shoe racks I could find, so I decided to just go for it. My girlfriend assembled these in under 10 minutes and our closet is so much neater. JUST DO IT if you have a huge pile of shoes! They aren't insanely sturdy but they hold my boots (we wear a lot of boots) - they do their job. I would order again if needed :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: There is a big design flaw in this show wrack. You put it together in the middle, which is very difficult to do because the pieces don't exactly fit well together, and it collapses in the middle due to the weight of the shoes. I have small feet and didn't even fill the entire wrack so there wasn't much weight on it considering it's a shoe wrack but it still collapsed in the middle after a couple months of use.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Sturdiness is, well, less than satisfactory
reviews.reviewText: I don’t think I have written a review for anything before but this shoe rack really has me going. It’s not THAT deep because, I mean, it’s a shoe rack, but I have been in a 5 month battle with this thing. I will say, it looks really nice when it is staying together but that is approximately 44% of the time. The middle connectors I feel have a personal vendetta against me since they do not actually keep the both sides together. I have like 3 pairs of shoes on it but GOD FORBID the pressure was too much for this little guy. Anywho, don’t really recommend 👍

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Does the job
reviews.reviewText: This rack does what it is supposed to. No more, no less. Easy to assemble and fits 6 pairs of shoes on it and three under it. More if you have littles. Would not suggest putting anything heavy on it as it is only for shoes
